हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description:
Alia has a one-night stand before her first day at her dream job — only to discover her new boss is Adwait Patel, the same man from that night. As Adwait falls hard and tries to win her over, Alia must choose between keeping it professional or following her heart.

Will she risk everything for love… or protect her dreams?
